original_title: The Contagious Apparitions of Dambarey Dendrite
overview: Dambarey is a street kid, who in a dendrite induced trance, turns invincible to outfox Kathmandu with his gang of five. Little does he know that his altered mind is playing wicked tricks to lead him and his friends to a place of no return.
title: The Contagious Apparitions of Dambarey Dendrite
